=== “我是医生，不是……” ===

麦科伊多次使用的“我是医生，不是……”（{{Small|I'm a doctor, not a(n)...}}）句式是《星际旅行》的另一句流行语。<ref name="Butt">{{cite book|last=Butt|first=Miriam|coauthors=Kyle Wohlmut|others=Natascha Gentz (ed.), Stefan Kramer (ed.)|title=Globalization, Cultural Identities, and Media Representations|year=2006|publisher=SUNY Press|isbn=0791466833|page=83|chapter=The Thousand Faces of Xena: Transculturality Through Multi-Identity|chapterurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=GWyF18r-tR4C&pg=PA83|accessdate=2009-04-07|quote=each character's role is clearly defined by his or her position on the ship, so much so that one of the show's many catchphrases was Dr. McCoy's recurring line, 'I'm a doctor, not a . . .'|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805003236/https://books.google.com/books?id=GWyF18r-tR4C&pg=PA83|dead-url=no}}</ref>在许多集中，当麦科伊必须执行与医学技能不相关的任务时，他就会说出这句话；比如在〈{{TOS|Devil in the Dark}}〉（1967年）一集中，当他面对着罕见的[[硅|硅]]基外星人“霍塔”时，就出现了这样的“经典场景”。<ref>原文：“classic moment”．</ref><ref name="Lass">{{cite book|last=Lass|first=Martin|coauthors=Rickie Hilder|title=Musings of a Rogue Comet: Chiron, Planet of Healing|edition=2nd|year=2002|publisher=Galactic Publications|isbn=097159242X|page=212|chapter=The Discovery of Chiron|chapterurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=UiYNPFOnLLwC&pg=PA212|accessdate=2009-04-07|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804091319/https://books.google.com/books?id=UiYNPFOnLLwC&pg=PA212|dead-url=no}}<br />引文：“有一处经典场景（{{《}}{{TOS|Devil in the Dark}}{{》}}一集），当麦科伊要去执行一项挑战性的任务——去治愈一头主要由石块而不是血肉构成的生物时，他大叫到：‘我是医生，不是砖匠！’”<br />原文：“In a classic moment (episode: 'The Devil in the Dark'), McCoy, challenged with healing a being that was made more of rock than flesh, spouts out, 'I'm a doctor, not a bricklayer!'”</ref>《[[星际旅行：深空九号|星际旅行：深空九号]]》中的医生[[朱利安·巴希尔|朱利安·巴希尔]]（[[亚历山大·希迪希|亚历山大·希迪希]]）与《[[星际旅行：航海家号|星际旅行：航海家号]]》中的[[医生_(星际旅行)|医生]]（[[罗伯特·皮卡尔多|罗伯特·皮卡尔多]]）都曾使用过该句式的变体；此外，还有许多其他的电视剧使用了该句式，例如《[[神秘博士|神秘博士]]》、<ref name="VanHeerden">{{cite book|last=Van Heerden|first=Bill|title=Film and Television In-Jokes|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=l5RZAAAAMAAJ|accessdate=2009-04-07|publisher=McFarland|isbn=0786404566|page=227|quote=The Doctor has often used the "I'm a doctor, not a..." line popularized in the original Star Trek series by Dr. McCoy.|date=July 1998|archive-date=2015-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326211350/http://books.google.com/books?id=l5RZAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>《{{link-en|星际之门：亚特兰蒂斯|Stargate Atlantis}}》<ref name="SGA-Brotherhood">{{cite episode|title=The Brotherhood|series=''Stargate: Atlantis''|network=Sci Fi Channel|airdate=2005-01-03|season=1|number=14}}</ref>以及《[[机器鸡|机器鸡]]》。<ref name="RobChick">{{cite episode|title=The Munnery|episodelink=The Munnery|series=''Robot Chicken''|network=Cartoon Network|airdate=2006-09-24|season=2|number=12}}</ref>

